{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-66-diophantine-equation","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 66: Mlinganyo wa Diophantine","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotrite Diofantovu jednačinu drugog stepena tipa:</p>\n<div style='text-align: center;'>x<sup>2</sup> – Dy<sup>2</sup> = 1</div>\n<p>Na primer, kada je D = 13, najmanje rešenje za x je 649<sup>2</sup> − 13×180<sup>2</sup> = 1.</p>\n<p>Pretpostavlja se da nema rešenja u pozitivnim celim brojevima kada je D kvadrat.</p>\n<p>Dobijanjem najmanjeg rešenja za x kada je D = {2, 3, 5, 6, 7}, dobijamo sledeće:</p>\n<div style='margin-left: 2em;'>\n  3<sup>2</sup> – 2×2<sup>2</sup> = 1<br>\n  2<sup>2</sup> – 3×1<sup>2</sup> = 1<br>\n  <strong><span style='color: red;'>9</span></strong><sup>2</sup> – 5×4<sup>2</sup> = 1<br>\n  5<sup>2</sup> – 6×2<sup>2</sup> = 1<br>\n  8<sup>2</sup> – 7×3<sup>2</sup> = 1<br>\n</div>\n<p>Dakle, posmatrajući najmanje rešenje za <code>x</code> kada je D ≤ 7, najveća vrednost <code>x</code> dobija se za D = 5.</p>\n<p>Pronađi vrednost D ≤ <code>n</code> za koju najmanje rešenje za <code>x</code> daje najveću vrednost <code>x</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3ae1000cf542c50fec1","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302178,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-66-diophantine-equation"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function diophantineEquation(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ndiophantineEquation(7);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>diophantineEquation(7)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof diophantineEquation(7) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>diophantineEquation(7)</code> treba da vrati <code>5</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(diophantineEquation(7), 5);"},{"text":"<p><code>diophantineEquation(100)</code> treba da vrati <code>61</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(diophantineEquation(100), 61);"},{"text":"<p><code>diophantineEquation(409)</code> treba da vrati <code>409</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(diophantineEquation(409), 409);"},{"text":"<p><code>diophantineEquation(500)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>421</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(diophantineEquation(500), 421);"},{"text":"<p><code>diophantineEquation(1000)</code> treba da vrati <code>661</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(diophantineEquation(1000), 661);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-66-diophantine-equation","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-67-maximum-path-sum-ii","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-65-convergents-of-e","id":"5900f3ae1000cf542c50fec1","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-66-diophantine-equation"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}